\id EZR Ezra in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08 
\h Ɛzala 
\toc1 Ɛzala 
\toc2 Ɛzala 
\toc3 Ɛza 
\mt1 ƐZALA 
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ 
\ip Pɛɛsiↄ kí Kilusi Yudaↄ gbà zɛ́ aa gɛ́ Dii kpɛ́ kɛkɛ dↄi Yelusalɛũ (1). Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wà tàńnↄ yãa Babiloniↄ ɛ̀a lɛ́ tá ń bɛ (2). Yã́ sɛ̃́ia pↄ́ aa kɛ̀ an ɛa sua guu mɛ́ Lua gbagbakĩi kɛkɛ boa ũ, kɛ́ wàli e wàↄ sa'owà lán yãawa (3). Ãma Lua kpɛ́ kɛkɛ dↄa yã́ musu buipãleↄ íbɛlɛsɛ̀ńnↄ, ↄ̃ aa lɛ́kpãsãkɛ̀ Pɛɛsi gbãadeↄnɛ, kɛ́ wà e dↄ̃ tó aa ń gbá zɛ́ wà kpɛ́pi dↄ sĩanaɛ (4-6). 
\ip Bee gbɛa Pɛɛsiↄ kí Aatasasa sa'ona Ɛzala zĩ̀ we, ↄ̃ à lousisiyã vù Yelusalɛũ, a tò Yudaↄ nↄ̀sɛlìlɛ aa Lua yã́ kũ̀ ↄplapla. (7-10). 
\ip Ɛzala lá gbãakpà luanaaikɛa yã́waɛ ń kua gbãsĩsaio. Sa'ona Ɛzala wↄ́ↄ vĩ, ↄ̃ á kↄaikɛ̀ a tò gbɛ̃́ↄ nↄ̀sɛlìlɛ wà gↄ̃̀ luayãmanaↄ ũ. Ɛzala gↄↄ ↄ̃ Yudaↄ kɛ̀kɛ wà lousisiyã kũ̀ ↄplapla. Wɛ̃ↄ gɛ̃̀ dasi, a gbɛa ↄ̃ wà Yesu Kilisi ì. 
\c 1  
\s1 Kilusi Isailiↄ gbaɛa 
\p  
\v 1 Pɛɛsiↄ kí Kilusi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ sɛ̃́ia guu Dii tɛkpàaàgu, kɛ́ yã́ pↄ́ a dà Zelemiiɛ a ò e kɛ yã́i.\f + \fr 1.1 \ft Zel 25.11, 29.10\f* Ɔ̃ Kilusi kpàwakɛ̀ a bùsuu píi, ↄ̃ à gbàsa kɛ̃̀ láu à mɛ̀:  
\v 2 Yã́ pↄ́ ma Kilusi, Pɛɛsiↄ kía má òn kɛ: Dii Lua Musude tò dṹnia kpala píi gↄ̃̀ ma pↄ́ ũ, ↄ̃ a dìlɛmɛɛ mà kpɛdↄɛ Yelusalɛũ, Yuda bùsuu.\f + \fr 1.2 \ft Isa 44.28\f* 
\v 3 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ aà gbɛ̃́ ũ á guu, Lua kuaànↄ, i ta Yelusalɛũ, Yuda bùsuu, i kpɛdↄ Dii Isailiↄ Lua pↄ́ dɛ Dii ũ Yelusalɛũɛ we.  
\v 4 An gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gↄ̃̀piↄ saɛdeↄ dↄńlɛ ń ã́nusuo ń vuao ń àizɛɛↄ ń pↄtuoↄ ń Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ aalɛ gɛ́ dↄi Yelusalɛũ gbaↄ. 
\p  
\v 5 Ɔ̃ Yudaↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ uabeleↄ ń sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua tɛkpàńguↄ fɛ̀lɛ lɛ́ gɛ́ Dii kpɛ́ dↄi Yelusalɛũ.  
\v 6 An saɛdeↄ ↄdàmá, aa ń gbá ã́nusu pↄ́ↄ ń vua pↄ́ↄ ń àizɛɛↄ ń pↄtuoↄ ń pↄ́ ↄdeↄ ń Dii kpɛ́ gbaↄ píi.  
\v 7 Ɔ̃ Pɛɛsiↄ kí Kilusi bↄ̀ ń Dii kpɛ́ pↄ́ pↄ́ Nɛbukanɛza sɛ̀lɛ yãa Yelusalɛũ a kàlɛ a tã́a kpɛ́uↄ.  
\v 8 A ò a ↄ'ulɛna Miledaɛ aà pↄ́piↄ nao aà kpa Yudaↄ kí Sesebazaawa, ↄ̃ a kɛ̀ màa.  
\v 9 Pↄ́piↄ dasin kɛ: Vua ta baakwi, ã́nusu ta ↄ̀aa sↄo, tapɛlɛnti baakwi mɛ̀ndosai,  
\v 10 vua imibↄ baakwi, ã́nusu imibↄ ↄ̀aa pla ń kwio, ta buipãle ↄ̀aa sↄo.  
\v 11 Vua ń ã́nusu taↄ fɛ̀lɛ píi ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sↄo ń ↄ̀aa plao (5.400). Kɛ́ zĩ̀zↄpiↄ bↄ̀lɛ Babɛli aa sù Yelusalɛũ, ↄ̃ Sesebazaa mↄ̀ ń pↄ́piↄ píi. 
\c 2  
\s1 Zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Babɛli kí Nɛbukanɛza Isailiↄ kũ̀kũ zĩ̀zↄↄ ũ yãa, à tàńnↄ Babɛli, ↄ̃ an gbɛ̃eↄ bↄ̀ zĩ̀zↄkɛpiu aa sù Yelusalɛũ, Yuda bùsuu sa, ↄ̃ baade tà a bɛ wɛ̃́lɛu.  
\v 2 An dↄaanaↄn kɛ: Zolobabɛli, Yesua, Nɛɛmii, Selaia, Leelaia, Maadose, Bilisã, Misipaa, Bigivai, Leuũ ń Baanao. Isaili gↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ sùↄ dasilɛn kɛ: 
\p  
\v 3 Palↄsi buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ pla ń baswaaↄ̃kwi ń plao (2.172).  
\v 4 Sefatia buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń baswaaↄ̃kwi ń plao (372).  
\v 5 Ala buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń baswaaↄ̃kwi ń sↄoo (775).  
\v 6 Paata Mↄabu bui pↄ́ dɛ Yesua ń Yoabuo buiↄ ũↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ pla ń ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃ ń kuɛplao (2.812).  
\v 7 Elaũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa soolo ń blakwi ń síiↄ̃o (1.254).  
\v 8 Zatu buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃ ń basoplasↄoo (945).  
\v 9 Zakai buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń baswaaↄ̃o (760).  
\v 10 Bani buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń bla ń plao (642).  
\v 11 Bebai buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń bao ń àaↄ̃o (623).  
\v 12 Azegada buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa soolo ń bao ń plao (1.222).  
\v 13 Adonikaũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń bàaↄ̃sↄo ń mɛ̀ndoo (666).  
\v 14 Bigivai buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ pla ń bàaↄ̃ síiↄ̃saio (2.056).  
\v 15 Adini buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa pla ń blakwi ń síiↄ̃o (454).  
\v 16 Atee buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄo plasai (98).  
\v 17 Bezai buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basoolo ń àaↄ̃o (323).  
\v 18 Yola buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄokwi ń plao (112).  
\v 19 Asuũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń bao ń àaↄ̃o (223).  
\v 20 Gibaa buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄo sↄosai (95). 
\p  
\v 21 Bɛtɛlɛũdeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basoolo ń àaↄ̃o (123).  
\v 22 Nɛtofadeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃ síiↄ̃sai (56).  
\v 23 Anatodeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basoolosↄo ń àaↄ̃o (128).  
\v 24 Azemavɛdeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bla ń plao (42).  
\v 25 Kiliayaaliũdeↄ ń Kefiladeↄ ń Beelodeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń basopla ń àaↄ̃o (743).  
\v 26 Lamadeↄ ń Gɛbadeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń bao ń mɛ̀ndoo (621).  
\v 27 Mimasadeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basoolo ń plao (122).  
\v 28 Bɛtɛlideↄ ń Aideↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń bao ń àaↄ̃o (223).  
\v 29 Nɛbodeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn blakwi ń plao (52).  
\v 30 Magbisideↄ gbɛ̃ↄn baswaaↄ̃ síiↄ̃sai (156).  
\v 31 Elaũ pãle buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa soolo ń blakwi ń síiↄ̃o (1.254).  
\v 32 Aliũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basooloo (320).  
\v 33 Lodideↄ ń Adidadeↄ ń Onↄdeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń basoolosↄoo (725).  
\v 34 Yelikodeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basoplasↄoo (345).  
\v 35 Senaadeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ àaↄ̃ ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń baakwio (3.630). 
\p  
\v 36 Sa'ona bui pↄ́ sùↄn kɛ: Yesua bui Yedaia buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃ ń baswaaↄ̃kwi ń àaↄ̃o (973).  
\v 37 Imɛɛ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa sↄo ń blakwi ń plao (1.052).  
\v 38 Pasuu buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa soolo ń blasↄo ń plao (1.247).  
\v 39 Aliũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa sↄo ń gɛ̃o ń plao (1.017). 
\p  
\v 40 Levii bui pↄ́ sùↄn kɛ: Odavia bui Yesua ń Kamiɛlio buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃kwi ń síiↄ̃o (74).  
\v 41 Asafa bui lɛ̀sinaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basoolosↄo ń àaↄ̃o (128).  
\v 42 Bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃ana pↄ́ dɛ Saluũ ń Ateeo ń Talemↄo ń Akubuo ń Atitao ń Sobaio bui ũↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basopla mɛ̀ndosai (139). 
\p  
\v 43 Gbɛ̃́ɛ beeↄ buiↄ mɛ́ Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ ũ: Ziha, Asufa, Tabao,  
\v 44 Kelosi, Siaa, Padoni,  
\v 45 Lebana, Agaba, Akubu,  
\v 46 Agabu, Salemai, Anana,  
\v 47 Gideli, Gaaa, Leaia,  
\v 48 Lezini, Nɛkoda, Gaaũ,  
\v 49 Uza, Pasea, Besai,  
\v 50 Asena, Mɛuniũ, Nɛfusiũ,  
\v 51 Babuku, Akufa, Aluu,  
\v 52 Bazelu, Mɛida, Aasa,  
\v 53 Baakosi, Sisela, Tɛma,  
\v 54 Nɛzia ń Atifao. 
\p  
\v 55 Gbɛ̃́ɛ beeↄ mɛ́ Salomↄↄ zↄ̀blenaↄ buiↄ ũ: Sotai, Sofɛlɛ, Peludao,  
\v 56 Yala, Daakↄ̃, Gideli,  
\v 57 Sefatia, Atili, Pokɛlɛ Azebaiũ ń Amio.  
\v 58 Lua ua zĩkɛnapiↄ ń Salomↄↄ zↄ̀blenapiↄ kà gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa pla swaaↄ̃sai (392). 
\p  
\v 59 Gbɛ̃eↄ bↄ̀ Tɛmɛla ń Tɛlaasao ń Kelubuo ń Adↄ̃o ń Imɛɛo, ↄ̃ aai e ń buibↄkĩi ònɛ́o, tó Isailiↄn ń ũ.  
\v 60 Delaia ń Tobiao ń Nɛkodao buiↄnɛ, mɛ́ aa kà gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń blakwi ń plao (652).  
\v 61 Sa'ona bui pↄ́ dɛ Ɔbaia ń Akozio ń Baazilaio buiↄ ũ sù lↄ. Baazilaipi Galada bùsu gbɛ̃́ Baazilai nɛ́ sɛ̀ yãa, ↄ̃ à a ã̀nsuepi tↄ́ sɛ̀.  
\v 62 Gbɛ̃́piↄ ń tↄ́ wɛ̀ɛlɛ buibↄkĩi taalau, kási aai bↄwào, ↄ̃ wà gìnɛ́ ń sa'ozĩo.  
\v 63 Bùsu dↄaana ònɛ́, mɛ́ i kɛ sa'ona ń yã́ gwà ń Uliũo ń Tumiũo\f + \fr 2.63 \ft Bↄa 28.30, Iko 33.8\f* bàasio, aasu sa'oblɛ bleo. 
\p  
\v 64 Gbɛ̃́piↄ píi gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bla ń plao ń ↄ̀aa doo ń baswaaↄ̃oɛ (42.360).  
\v 65 An zↄ̀blenaↄ gↄ̃ɛ ń nↄɛo ku lↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sopla ń ↄ̀aa doo ń basopla àaↄ̃saio (7.337). Lɛ̀sinaↄ gↄ̃ɛ ń nↄɛo kúńnↄ lↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do.  
\v 66 Aa sↄ̃́ vĩ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń basopla síiↄ̃saio (736), sↄ̃baona ↄ̀aa do ń blasↄoo,  
\v 67 yiongo ↄ̀aa pla ń bla sↄosaio (435), zàa'ĩna ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ soolo ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃o ń basooloo (6.720). 
\p  
\v 68 Kɛ́ aa kà Dii kpɛ́ dↄkĩi Yelusalɛũ, an uabeleeↄ gbadàda, kɛ́ aa e Lua kpɛ́ kɛkɛ dↄò a gbɛu.  
\v 69 Aa gbadà kpɛ́ zĩ kpagolo guu ń gbãa lɛ́u, vua kiloo ↄ̀aa pla ń basↄoo (500), ã́nusu tↄnu àaↄ̃ ń sa'ona ulataoↄ basↄo.  
\v 70 Sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń lɛ̀sinaↄ ń bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ń Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ ń gbɛ̃pãleeↄ zↄ̃̀lɛzↄ̃lɛ wɛ̃́lɛ pↄ́ wa kɛ̀kɛnɛ́ↄ guu, ↄ̃ Isaili kĩniↄ zↄ̃̀lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guu.\f + \fr 2.70 \ft 1Lad 9.2-3, Nɛɛ 11.1-3\f* 
\c 3  
\s1 Dii gbagbakĩi boa 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ wɛ̃̀ mↄ soplade kà, Isailiↄ sù zↄ̃̀lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guu píi. Ɔ̃ aa kã̀aa Yelusalɛũ lán gbɛ̃́ mɛ̀ndowa.  
\v 2 Yozada nɛ́ Yesua ń a sa'on deeↄ ń Salatiɛli nɛ́ Zolobabɛlio ń a gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄ Lua gbagbakĩi bò, kɛ́ aa sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ owà, lá Lua gbɛ̃́ Mↄizi ò a ikoyã guuwa.  
\v 3 Baa kɛ́ aalɛ vĩakɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú bùsupi guuↄnɛ, aa gbagbakĩipi bò a gbɛuɛ, ↄ̃ aa sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ ò Diiwa kↄↄ ń oosio.\f + \fr 3.3 \ft Nao 28.1-8\f* 
\v 4 Aa Lákpɛdↄa dikpɛkɛ̀ lá a ku lápi guuwa, aaìↄ sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ o lá gu lɛ́ dↄ, lá wà a lɛ́ dìlɛwa.\f + \fr 3.4 \ft Nao 29.12-38\f* 
\v 5 Bee gbɛa aa sa pↄ́ wìↄ o gↄↄpii ò ń mↄ dafu pↄ́o ń dikpɛ pↄ́ Dii dìlɛↄ pↄ́o ń gba pↄ́ wì mↄoɛ̀ↄ.\f + \fr 3.5 \ft Nao 28.11-29.11\f* 
\v 6 Mↄ soplade gↄↄ sɛ̃́ia zĩ́ ↄ̃ aa nà Dii gbagbaawa màa, baa kɛ́ wi aà kpɛ́ dↄ yãao. 
\p  
\v 7 Aa ↄ̃a kpà gbɛ̀'ãnaↄ ń li'ãnaↄwa, ↄ̃ aa pↄblea ń imiao ń nísio kpà Sidↄ̃deↄ ń Tiideↄwa, kɛ́ aa sɛdɛ lí zↄ̃zↄ̃ Libã bùsuu, aa yeye gɛò Zope daa ísiaa, lá Pɛɛsiↄ kía Kilusi ń gbá zɛ́wa.  
\v 8 An kaa Lua kpɛ́ dↄkĩi Yelusalɛũ wɛ̃̀ plaade mↄ plaade guu, Salatiɛli nɛ́ Zolobabɛli ń Yozada nɛ́ Yesuao nà zĩwa ń ń gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ, sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ bↄ̀ zĩ̀zↄkɛu aa sù Yelusalɛũↄ píi. Aa Levii bui pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ bao ge aa dɛaↄ dìlɛ Dii kpɛ́ zĩpi gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ũ.  
\v 9 Yesua ń a buiↄ nàkↄ̃wa ń Kamiɛlio ń aà nɛ́ Odavia buiↄ, ↄ̃ aa gↄ̃̀ zĩpi gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ũ ń Enadao ń aà buiↄ. Levii buiↄnɛ ḿpii.  
\v 10 Kɛ́ Dii kpɛbonaↄ lɛ́ kpɛ́pi ɛ̃ kpálɛ, sa'onaↄ zɛzɛ we sa'on pↄkasaↄ dadaa, aa ń kuuↄ kṹkũa, mɛ́ Levii nɛ́ Asafa buiↄ ku we lↄ ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ aa Dii táasilɛò, lá Isailiↄ kí Davidi ò yãawa.\f + \fr 3.10 \ft 1Lad 25.1\f* 
\v 11 Aa lɛsì aa Dii táasilɛ̀, aa aà sáaukpà aa mɛ̀: Dii maa, aà gbɛ̃kɛkɛa wá Isailiↄnɛ láaa vĩo. Ɔ̃ gbɛ̃́pii wii gbãa lɛ̀ aa Dii táasilɛ̀, kɛ́ wà Dii kpɛ́ ɛ̃ kpàlɛ yã́i.  
\v 12 Kási sa'on daside ń Levii buiↄ ń uabele pↄ́ zikũ̀ aa wɛsì kpɛ́ káaulɛↄ, kɛ́ aa kpɛ́pi ɛ̃boa è, aa búbuapɛ̀ɛ. Gbɛ̃́ dasideↄ sↄ̃ aalɛ pↄna wii lɛ.  
\v 13 Gbɛ̃e pↄna wii dↄ̃kↄ̃ɛ ń búbua pↄ́ wàlɛ pɛ́o lↄo, kɛ́ baade lɛ́ wii gbãa lɛ yã́i, mɛ́ wà kↄ̃fĩpi mà zã̀. 
\c 4  
\s1 Íbɛlɛsɛa ń Dii kpɛbonaↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ Yudaↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ ibɛɛↄ mà zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ lɛ́ kpɛ́ bo Dii Isailiↄ Luaɛ,  
\v 2 aa mↄ̀ Zolobabɛli ń uabeleↄ lè, aa ònɛ́: À to wà kpɛ́ boánↄ, asa wi á Lua kĩ́i wɛɛlɛ lááwa sↄ̃ɛ. Wiↄ aà gbagbaɛ za gↄↄ pↄ́ Asiliↄ kí Esaadↄ̃ sùwanↄ la.\f + \fr 4.2 \ft 2Kia 17.24-41\f* 
\v 3 Ɔ̃ Zolobabɛli ń Yesuao ń Isaili uabele kĩniↄ ònɛ́: Wá Lua kpɛ́ boa dɛ á yã́ ũo. Wá wá pↄ́ bo Dii Isailiↄ Luaɛ wátɛ̃ɛ, lá Pɛɛsiↄ kí Kilusi dìlɛwɛ̃ɛwaɛ.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ bùsupideↄ lɛ́ wɛɛlɛ Yudaↄ kãdɛ, aalɛ ĩadamá, kɛ́ aasu kpɛ́pi boo yã́i.  
\v 5 Aa fĩabò kía lɛdamadeↄnɛ za Kilusi gↄↄ e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Pɛɛsiↄ kí Daliusi kpalablegↄↄwa, ↄ̃ aa gìnɛ́ ń yã́ pↄ́ aalɛ yáo. 
\p  
\v 6 Aa lakɛ̃ Aasueluɛ\f + \fr 4.6 \ft Ɛsi 1.1\f* aà kpalablea daalɛgↄↄ, aa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũↄ ń Yuda bùsuo píi káalakɛ̀ɛ̀.  
\v 7 Biselaũ ń Miledao ń Tabeelio ń ń gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ lakɛ̃ Pɛɛsiↄ kí Aatasasaɛ lↄ aà kpalablegↄↄ. Aa kɛ̃̀ɛ̀ ń Sili yã́o, ↄ̃ wà a bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ɛ̀.  
\v 8 Bùsu gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ Leuũ ń a lakɛ̃na Simɛsaio lakɛ̃ kí Aatasasaɛ Yelusalɛũ yã́ musu lↄ aa mɛ̀:  
\v 9 Bùsu gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ Leuũ ń a lakɛ̃na Simɛsaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ kĩni Dinadeↄ ń Afaasatadeↄ ń Taapɛlideↄ ń Afaasideↄ ń Ɛlɛkideↄ ń Babɛlideↄ ń Susade pↄ́ bↄ̀lɛ Elaũ bùsuuↄ  
\v 10 ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kía zↄ̃ↄ bɛɛɛde Asenapa ń bↄ́lɛ ń bùsuu aa ń zↄ̃́lɛzↄ̃lɛ Samali wɛ̃́lɛu ń Uflata baala gupãleuↄ,  
\v 11 wá Uflata baaladeↄ n zↄ̀blenaↄ mɛ́ lápi kɛ̃̀nɛ kí Aatasasa, wa mɛ̀: 
\p  
\v 12 Kí, ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ kɛ́ Yuda pↄ́ bↄ̀ n kĩ́i aa sù laↄ gɛ̀ lɛ́ Yelusalɛũ wɛ̃́lɛ vãi pãsĩpi kálɛ, aa ɛ̀a lɛ́ a bĩ́ibo lↄ, aalɛ a bɛzia fɛlɛ.  
\v 13 Kí, ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ lↄ, tó aa ɛ̀a wɛ̃́lɛpi kàlɛ aa a bĩ́ibò wa làa, aa falubↄnɛ lↄo ge ɛlɛ'ↄ̃a ge wɛ̃̀'ↄ̃a, aai n ↄ̃a pↄ́ ni si kɛ̃́sã.  
\v 14 Tia kɛ́wa kí, lá ḿmɛ ń wá ũ, i kũ wà n kpɛ eo. A yã́i wa láɛ bee kpã̀sãinɛ kɛ́ wà yã́pi onɛ.  
\v 15 Wɛɛlɛ n deziↄ láↄ guu ǹ gwa, ní e dↄ̃ lá wɛ̃́lɛpideↄ swã́ gbãa, aa ĩadà kíaↄwa ń bùsu gbãadeↄ. Za zi wɛ̃́lɛpideↄ yãkele kɛ̀ zài. Bee yã́ mɛ́ tò wà wɛ̃́lɛpi dúuzↄ̃̀i.  
\v 16 Kí, wálɛ onɛ, tó wà ɛ̀a wɛ̃́lɛpi fɛ̀lɛ, wà ɛ̀a a bĩ́ibò wa làa, ńyↄ̃ↄ pↄe vĩ Uflata baala lↄo. 
\p  
\v 17 Bee gbɛa kía lá kpã̀sãnɛ́ à mɛ̀: Bùsu gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ Leuũ ń a lakɛ̃na Simɛsaio ń á gbɛ̃́ kĩni pↄ́ kú Samali ń Uflata baaleↄ, ma fↄkpàwá.  
\v 18 Lá pↄ́ á kpã̀sãmɛɛ, wà a kyokɛ̀ wà a bↄↄlɛkɛ̀mɛɛ.  
\v 19 Má ò wà wɛɛlɛ lá ziↄ guu, ↄ̃ wa è sĩanaɛ, wɛ̃́lɛpideↄ ìↄ bↄ kíaↄ kpɛɛ. Za zi yãkeledeↄnɛ.  
\v 20 Kía zↄ̃ↄↄ kpalablè Yelusalɛũ we, aa gbãablè Uflata baaledeↄwa píi, wà falubↄ̀nɛ́ ń ɛlɛ'ↄ̃ao ń wɛ̃̀'ↄ̃ao.  
\v 21 À yãdilɛ gbɛ̃́piↄnɛ aa kã́mabo sa. Aasu ɛa wɛ̃́lɛpi vuo e mà ń gba lɛ́.  
\v 22 À laaika! Ásu niazĩkpa yã́pizio, kɛ́ vãipi su ↄta, aa wá ásookɛo yã́i. 
\p  
\v 23 Kɛ́ wà kí Aatasasa lápi kyokɛ̀, wà a bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ Leuũɛ ń a lakɛ̃na Simɛsaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ, ↄ̃ aa fɛ̀lɛ gɛ̀ Yudaↄ lè Yelusalɛũ gↄ̃̀ↄ. Aa gìnɛ́ pãsĩpãsĩ aa mɛ̀ aa kã́mabo.  
\v 24 Beewa aa kã́mabò ń Lua kpɛ́ zĩ pↄ́ aalɛ kɛ Yelusalɛũo e Pɛɛsiↄ kí Daliusi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ plaade guu. 
\c 5  
\s1 Tatɛnai lákɛ̃a kí Daliusiɛ 
\p  
\v 1 Ãnabi Age\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Age 1.1\f* ń ãnabi Zakali,\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Zkl 1.1\f* Ido nɛ́o ãnabikɛkɛ̀ Yuda pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũↄ ń Yuda bùsuo píi ń Isailiↄ Lua tↄ́o.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ Salatiɛli nɛ́ Zolobabɛli ń Yozada nɛ́ Yesuao fɛ̀lɛ nà Lua kpɛ́ boawa Yelusalɛũ.\f + \fr 5.2 \ft Age 1.12\f* Lua ãnabipiↄ kúńnↄ, aalɛ dↄńlɛ.\f + \fr 5.2 \ft Zkl 4.6-9\f* 
\v 3 Wegↄ̃ↄ Uflata baala dↄaana Tatɛnai ń Setaa Bozenaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ mↄ̀ ń lé, aa ń lá aa mɛ̀: Démɛ á gbá zɛ́ à kpɛ́ɛ bee kɛkɛ boi?  
\v 4 Aa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ kpɛ́pi boↄ tↄ́ gbɛ̀a lↄ.  
\v 5 Ń beeo Lua lɛ́ wɛ́tɛ Yuda gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄpiↄzi, ↄ̃ aai onɛ́ aa kã́maboo. Aa mɛ̀ wà lɛ́kpãsãkɛ Daliusiɛ gĩa, aai lá pↄ́ a kɛ̃ a yã́ musu e.  
\v 6 Uflata baala dↄaana Tatɛnai ń Setaa Bozenaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ Pɛɛsi buiↄ lakɛ̃, ↄ̃ aa kpã̀sã kí Daliusiɛ.  
\v 7 Lɛ́kpãsã pↄ́ aa kɛ̀ɛ̀n kɛ, aa mɛ̀: 
\p Kí Daliusi, wa fↄkpàma maamaa.  
\v 8 Kí, ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ kɛ́ wa gɛ Yuda bùsuu e Lua zↄ̃ↄde kpɛ́u. Wàlɛ kpɛ́pi bo ń gbɛ̀ gbɛ̃̀nɛↄ, wàlɛ lí da kpɛ́pi gĩↄwa. Wàlɛ zĩpi kɛ ń laaio, àlɛ táa'o.  
\v 9 Wa yãlàla ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄwa wa mɛ̀: Démɛ á gbá zɛ́ à kpɛ́ɛ bee kɛkɛ boi?  
\v 10 Wa ń tↄ́ gbɛ̀a kɛ́ wà e onɛ, ↄ̃ wa ń dↄaanapiↄ tↄ́ dàlau.  
\v 11 Lá aa yã́zãsìwán kɛ: Aa mɛ̀ musu ń zĩ́lɛo Lua zↄ̀blenaↄn ń ũ. Kpɛ́ pↄ́ wa bò yãa à wɛ̃ kɛ̀, ↄ̃ wa kɛ̀kɛ lɛ́ bo lↄ. Isailiↄ kí zↄ̃ↄ mɛ́ bò yãa.  
\v 12 Aa mɛ̀ ń deziↄ Lua Musude pↄ fɛ̀lɛ, ↄ̃ à ń ná Babiloni bui Nɛbukanɛza, Babɛli kíaɛ a ↄzĩ, ↄ̃ à kpɛ́pi wìwi à gbɛ̃́piↄ sɛ̀lɛ tàńnↄ Babɛli.\f + \fr 5.12 \ft 2Kia 25.8-12\f* 
\v 13 Bee gbɛa Babɛli kí Kilusi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ sɛ̃́ia guu à yãdìlɛ à mɛ̀ wà ɛa Lua kpɛ́pi bo lↄ.  
\v 14 Baa vua ń ã́nusu pↄ́ pↄ́ Nɛbukanɛza sɛ̀lɛ Lua kpɛ́u Yelusalɛũ, a kàlɛ a tã́akpɛu Babɛliↄ, kí Kilusi bↄ̀lɛ kpà Sesebazaa pↄ́ à aà dìlɛ bùsu dↄaana ũwaɛ.\f + \fr 5.14 \ft Ɛza 1.2-11\f* 
\v 15 A òɛ̀ aà pↄ́piↄ sɛ gɛ kálɛ Lua kpɛ́u Yelusalɛũ, tó wà kpɛ́pi kɛ̀kɛ dↄ̀.  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ Sesebazaa mↄ̀ Lua kpɛ́ ɛ̃ kpàlɛ. Wàlɛ kpɛ́pi bo za gↄↄ beeɛ e gbã, kási i láa yãao.  
\v 17 Kí, tó à kɛ̀nɛ maa, lá wɛɛlɛ kíaↄ lákalɛkĩi Babɛli, ní gwa tó kí Kilusi yãdìlɛ wà Lua kpɛ́ dↄ Yelusalɛũɛ. Lá ń è, ní lɛ́kpãsãkɛwɛ̃ɛ. 
\c 6  
\s1 Daliusi yãdilɛa Lua kpɛ́ boa yã́ musu 
\p  
\v 1 Kí Daliusi yãdìlɛ, ↄ̃ wà lápi wɛ̀ɛlɛ taala pↄ́ wa kàlɛ Babɛli lákalɛkĩiↄ guu.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ wà bↄ̀ lá kooawa Ɛbatana wɛ̃́lɛ bĩ́ideu Mɛdɛ bùsuu. Yã́ɛ bee ku a guu, kɛ́ asu sã́ńguo yã́i: 
\p  
\v 3 Kí Kilusi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ sɛ̃́ia guu à yãdìlɛ Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũ musu, à mɛ̀ wà kpɛ́pi dↄ sa'okĩi ũ. Wà a ɛ̃bo a lɛsĩ ká gã̀sĩsuu bàaↄ̃, a yàasa gã̀sĩsuu bàaↄ̃.  
\v 4 Wàli gbɛ̀ gbɛ̃̀nɛ di àaↄ̃, lí mɛ̀ndo, gbɛ̀ gbɛ̃̀nɛ àaↄ̃, lí mɛ̀ndo. Wa a fĩabo ń kibɛ ↄ̃ao.  
\v 5 Vua ń ã́nusu pↄ́ pↄ́ Nɛbukanɛza sɛ̀lɛ Lua kpɛ́u Yelusalɛũ à sùò Babɛliↄ sↄ̃, wa ɛa gɛ kálɛ a gbɛu Lua kpɛ́u Yelusalɛũ. 
\p  
\v 6 Ɔ̃ kí Daliusi lɛ́kpãsãkɛ̀ à mɛ̀: Tiasa Uflata baale dↄaana Tatɛnai ń Setaa Bozenaio ń á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú Uflata baa weↄ, à ázĩa ga we.  
\v 7 À Lua kpɛ́ dↄ̀na dãↄ to tɛɛɛ. À to Yudaↄ dↄaana ń ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ Lua kpɛ́pi kɛkɛ dↄ.  
\v 8 Málɛ yã́ pↄ́ ásu kɛ Yuda gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄnɛ Lua kpɛ́pi dↄa musu dilɛɛ́. À pↄ́ pↄ́ aa yeiↄ sɛ́lɛ ma làasiu we ń Uflata baale falu pↄ́ wa bↄ̀o, í kpámá píi, kɛ́ zĩpi su zɛ lↄo yã́i.  
\v 9 Pↄ́ pↄ́ aa yei píi, zugaae, sãsakao, sãnɛbↄlↄ pↄ́ aaì Lua Musude gbagbaò, pↄ́wɛna, wisi, vɛ̃ɛ, nísi, àↄ kpa Yelusalɛũ sa'onaↄwa lá gu lɛ́ dↄ lá aa gbɛ̀awáwa pãkpaisai,  
\v 10 kɛ́ aa e sa pↄ́ kà Lua Musudegu owà, aai wabikɛwàmɛɛ ń ma nɛ́ↄ.  
\v 11 Tó gbɛ̃e yã́ pↄ́ má dìlɛɛ bee lìlɛ, wa ade kpɛ́ lí wo, wi aà pawà wà pɛ́lɛ, wi aà bɛ kɛ tufua ũ.  
\v 12 Tó kíae ge buie lɛ́ wɛɛlɛ yã́pi lilɛ ge àlɛ wɛɛlɛ Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũpi wí, Lua pↄ́ tò a tↄ́ kú gupiwa, aà ade fu. Ma Daliusi mámɛ ma yã́pi dìlɛ. Wà zĩkɛwà maamaa. 
\s1 Lua kpɛ́ sakɛ̃a 
\p  
\v 13 Kɛ́ kí Daliusi lɛ́kpãsãpi kɛ̀ màa, Uflata baala dↄaana Tatɛnai ń Setaa Bozenaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ yã́pi kɛ̀ ń laaio.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ Yuda gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ kpɛdↄa lɛ́ gɛ́ aɛ lá ãnabi Age\f + \fr 6.14 \ft Age 1.1\f* ń ãnabi Zakali Ido nɛ́o\f + \fr 6.14 \ft Zkl 1.1\f* ãnabikɛkɛ̀wa. Aa kpɛ́pi dↄ̀ wa làa lá Isailiↄ Lua òwa, lá Pɛɛsiↄ kíaↄ Kilusi ń Daliusio ń Aatasasao a yãdìlɛwa.  
\v 15 Aa Lua kpɛ́ mìdɛ Adaa gↄↄ àaↄ̃de zĩ́ kí Daliusi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ soolode guuɛ.  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ Isailiↄ Lua kpɛ́ sakɛ̃̀ ń pↄnao, sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń gbɛ̃́ kĩni pↄ́ sù ń zĩ̀zↄkɛoↄ píi.  
\v 17 Lua kpɛ́ sakɛ̃api yã́i aa sa'ò ń zuswanaↄ mɛ̀n basↄo ń sãsakaoↄ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa do ń sãnɛbↄlↄↄ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa pla, ↄ̃ aa sa'ò ń blesanaↄ mɛ̀n kuɛpla Isaili bui dasilɛu ampii duun awakpabↄ ũ.  
\v 18 Aa sa'onaↄ dìlɛdilɛ gã ń gão, mɛ́ aa Levii buiↄ dìlɛdilɛ gã ń gão lↄ, kɛ́ aa zĩkɛ Luaɛ Yelusalɛũ, lá a ku Mↄizi lá guuwa. 
\p  
\v 19 Mↄ sɛ̃́ia gↄↄ gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosaide zĩ́, zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùpiↄ Gɛ̃amusu dikpɛ\f + \fr 6.19 \ft Bↄa 12.1-20\f* kɛ̀.  
\v 20 Sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ gbãbↄ̀ ńzĩaɛ aa gↄ̃̀ gbãlɛsai ḿpii, ↄ̃ aa Gɛ̃amusu sã kòlokpakpa zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄnɛ ń ń sa'on deeↄ pↄ́o ń ńzĩa pↄ́o.  
\v 21 Isaili zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùpiↄ mɛ́ sò ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa gbãlɛa buipãleↄ yã́ musu tò, aalɛ Dii Isailiↄ Lua kĩ́i wɛɛlɛↄ.  
\v 22 Ɔ̃ aa Kàaso dikpɛkɛ̀ ń pↄnao e gↄↄ sopla. Dii tò an pↄ kɛ̀na, asa a tò Asiliↄ kía nↄ̀sɛlìlɛ ń yã́ musuɛ, ↄ̃ à dↄ̀ńlɛ a kpɛdↄa zĩ guu, Isailiↄ Luapi. 
\c 7  
\s1 Ɛzala sua Yelusalɛũ sↄukɛa 
\p  
\v 1-5 Yã́ beeↄ gbɛa Pɛɛsiↄ kí Aatasasa kpalablegↄↄ Ɛzala bↄ̀ Babɛli à sù. Sa'onkia Aalona mɛ́ Ɛleazaa ì, Ɛleazaa Finɛasi ì, Finɛasi Abisua ì, Abisua Buki ì, Buki Uzi ì, Uzi Zelaia ì, Zelaia Mɛlaio ì, Mɛlaio Azalia ì, Azalia Amalia ì, Amalia Aitubu ì, Aitubu Zadoki ì, Zadoki Saluũ ì, Saluũ Ilikia ì, Ilikia Azalia ì, Azalia Selaia ì, ↄ̃ Selaia Ɛzalapi ì.  
\v 6 Ɛzalaá yãdanɛdeɛ, a Mↄizi ikoyã pↄ́ Dii Isailiↄ Lua dìlɛ dↄ̃ sã́asã. Lá Dii aà Lua ↄkùaàla, kía pↄ́ pↄ́ à a wabikɛ̀wa kpàwà píiɛ.  
\v 7 Kí Aatasasa kpalablea wɛ̃̀ soplade guu Isailieↄ sù Yelusalɛũ lↄ. Sa'onaↄ kú ń guu ń Levii buiↄ ń lɛ̀sinaↄ ń bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ń Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ.  
\v 8 Ɛzala kà Yelusalɛũ kí kpalablea wɛ̃̀ soplade mↄ sↄode guu.  
\v 9 À fɛ̀lɛ Babɛli mↄ sɛ̃́ia gↄↄ sɛ̃́ia zĩ́ɛ, ↄ̃ à kà Yelusalɛũ mↄ sↄode gↄↄ sɛ̃́iazĩ. Aà Lua ↄ kuaàla,  
\v 10 asa Ɛzala mɛkpà Dii ikoyã wàaipaawa ń a kɛao, kɛ́ à e aà yãdilɛnɛↄ ń aà ikoyãↄ dada Isailiↄnɛ. 
\s1 Lá pↄ́ kí Aatasasa kpà Ɛzalawa 
\p  
\v 11 Taala pↄ́ kí Aatasasa kpà sa'on Ɛzala pↄ́ ì Dii yãdilɛaↄ ń aà yãdilɛnɛↄ da Isailiↄnɛwa yã́n kɛ:  
\v 12 Aatasasa, kíaↄ kía mɛ́ láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ sa'ona Ɛzala, Lua Musude ikoyãdanaɛ. Ma fↄkpàma.  
\v 13 Ma yãdìlɛ ma mɛ̀ Isaili bui ge sa'ona ge Levii bui pↄ́ kú ma bùsuu aa ye gɛnnↄ Yelusalɛũↄ píi, aa gɛ́.  
\v 14 Mapi ń ma lɛdamade gbɛ̃ↄn soplaↄ mɛ́ n gbaɛ, kɛ́ ǹ gɛ́ Yelusalɛũ ń Yuda bùsuo píi yã́ gwagwai n Lua ikoyã pↄ́ ń kũa musu.  
\v 15 Ãnusu ń vua pↄ́ mapi ń ma lɛdamadeↄ wa Isailiↄ Lua pↄ́ aà bɛ ku Yelusalɛũ gbà sɛ́lɛ wà gɛò  
\v 16 ń ã́nusuo ń vua pↄ́ ń è Babɛli bùsuuo píi ń pↄ́ pↄ́ gbɛ̃́ↄ ń sa'onaↄ kpà ń Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ ũ Yelusalɛũo.  
\v 17 Zuswanaↄ ń sãsakaoↄ ń sãnɛbↄlↄↄ lúlu ń ↄ̃apio n laaiwa, ní sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ oò n Lua kpɛ́ gbagbakĩiwa Yelusalɛũ ń pↄ́wɛnti gbao ń imia gbao.  
\v 18 Mpi ń n gbɛ̃́ↄ à kɛ ń ã́nusuo ń vua pↄ́ gↄ̃̀o lá à kɛ̀ɛ́ maawa, lá á Lua yeiwa.  
\v 19 Pↄ́ pↄ́ wà nànɛ n ↄzĩ lousisia Lua kpɛ́u pↄ́ ũↄ kpa n Luapiwa Yelusalɛũ.  
\v 20 Tó ń ye Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ kĩniↄi, tó a kɛkɛa gↄ̃̀ n yã́ ũɛ, sɛ ma làasiu we.  
\v 21 Mámɛmaa kí Aatasasa, ma yãdìlɛ Uflata baale ↄ'ulɛnaↄnɛ píiɛ. À wabi pↄ́ sa'ona Ɛzala, Lua Musude ikoyãdana kɛ̀wá kpawà gↄ̃̀ↄ píi.  
\v 22 Ãnusu su dɛ tↄnu àaↄ̃ao. Pↄ́wɛna su dɛ tↄnu baakwiao. Vɛ̃ɛ ń nísio su dɛ litili ↄ̀aa baobaoao. Wisi sↄ̃, lá a yei lɛ́u.  
\v 23 Lá Lua Musude dìlɛ píi, à kpa gↄ̃̀ↄ aà kpɛ́ pↄ́ ũ, kɛ́ asu kpɛ̃nɛkɛ ń ma kíakɛo ge ma nɛ́ↄo.  
\v 24 Àↄ dↄ̃ sↄ̃ kɛ́ á zɛvĩ à falu ge ɛlɛ'ↄ̃a ge wɛ̃̀'ↄ̃a sí Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ ge sa'onaↄ ge Levii buiↄ ge lɛ̀sinaↄ ge bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ge zĩkɛnpãleↄwao. 
\p  
\v 25 Mpi sↄ̃ Ɛzala, yã́kpalɛkɛnaↄ ń yãgↄ̃gↄ̃naↄ dilɛdilɛ ↄ̃nↄ pↄ́ n Lua kpàma lɛ́u, kɛ́ aa yãkɛkɛ a zɛ́wa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú Uflata baaleↄnɛ píi. Aaↄ dɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa n Lua ikoyã dↄ̃ↄ ũ. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dↄ̃oↄ sↄ̃, dadanɛ́.  
\v 26 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ n Lua ikoyã ń bùsu ikoyão kũa ↄplaplao, wa yãdaaàla, aà dɛa ge aà ya bↄa bùsuu ge aà àizɛɛ siawà ge aà daakpɛun nò. 
\p  
\v 27 Ɔ̃ Ɛzala mɛ̀: Wà Dii wá deziↄ Lua sáaukpa! À làasoo maa dà kíɛ a sↄ̃u, ↄ̃ kípi gbãakpà aà kpɛ́ pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũwa màa.  
\v 28 A tò ma yã́ kà kía ń a lɛdamadeↄgu ń aà ìwa gbãaↄ píi. Lá Dii ma Lua ↄ kuamala, ma sↄ̃dìlɛ, ↄ̃ ma Isaili dↄaanaↄ kã̀aa aa gɛmanↄ. 
\c 8  
\s1 Uabele pↄ́ sù ń Ɛzalaoↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Uabele pↄ́ wa bↄ Babɛli bùsuu Aatasasa kpalablegↄↄ wa su sãnuↄ tↄ́ↄn kɛ ń ń buibↄkĩio: 
\q1  
\v 2 Finɛasi buiↄ uabele Geesoũ, 
\q1 Itamaa buiↄ uabele Daniɛli, 
\q1 Davidi buiↄ uabele Atusu. 
\q1  
\v 3 Palↄsi bui Zakali ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basoplakwi. 
\q1  
\v 4 Paata Mↄabu bui Zelaia nɛ́ Ɛlioenai ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do. 
\q1  
\v 5 Zatu bui Yaaziɛ nɛ́ Sekania ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basↄoo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Adini bui Yonatãa nɛ́ Ɛbɛdɛ ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn blakwi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Elaũ bui Atalia nɛ́ Yesaia ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃kwi. 
\q1  
\v 8 Sefatia bui Mikaila nɛ́ Zebadia ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basiiↄ̃. 
\q1  
\v 9 Yoabu bui Yeiɛli nɛ́ Obadia ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń gɛ̃o ń àaↄ̃o. 
\q1  
\v 10 Bani bui Yosifia nɛ́ Selomi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn baswaaↄ̃. 
\q1  
\v 11 Bebai bui Bebai nɛ́ Zakali ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn baasↄo ń àaↄ̃o. 
\q1  
\v 12 Azegada bui Akatã nɛ́ Yohanani ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄokwi. 
\q1  
\v 13 Adonikaũ bui pↄ́ sù gbɛzãↄ, Ɛlifele ń Yeiɛlio ń Semaiao ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃. 
\q1  
\v 14 Bigivai buiↄ Zakuu ń Utaio ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃kwi. 
\s1 Ɛzalaↄ daa Yelusalɛũ zɛ́u 
\p  
\v 15 Ma ń kãaa swa pↄ́ ì dↄ Aavai, ↄ̃ wa bòokpà we gↄↄ àaↄ̃. Kɛ́ ma gbɛ̃́ↄ fãnkɛ ń sa'onaↄ, má è Levii buiↄ kú ń guuo.  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ ma dↄaanaɛ beeↄ sìsi: Ɛliɛzɛɛ, Aliɛli, Semaia, Ɛlenatã, Yalibu, Ɛlenatã, Natã, Zakali ń Mɛsulaũo. Ma yãdanɛdeↄ Yoialibu ń Ɛlenatão sìsi lↄ.  
\v 17 Ma ń zĩ́ Ido pↄ́ dɛ dↄaana ũ gu pↄ́ wì mɛ Kasifia kĩ́i. Ma yã́ pↄ́ aa oɛ̀ ń aà gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú weↄ dànɛ́, kɛ́ aa suwɛ̃ɛ ń wá Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ.  
\v 18 Lá wá Lua ↄ kuawála maannↄ, aa sùwɛ̃ɛ ń gbɛ̃́ laaideo, Levii tↄũna Mali bui Selebia ń aà nɛ́ↄ ń aà dãunaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bao plasai.  
\v 19 Aa sù ń Mɛlali buiↄ Asabia ń Yesaiao lↄ ń ń dãunaↄ ń ń nɛ́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bao.  
\v 20 Aa sù ń Lua ua zĩkɛna pↄ́ Davidi ń a ìwaↄ ń dílɛ aa dↄ Levii buiↄlɛↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń baoo. Wà ń tↄ́ dàlau ḿpii. 
\p  
\v 21 Ma lɛye kpàwakɛ̀ Aava swa saɛ we, kɛ́ wà wázĩa busa wá Luaɛ, wí tá na wabikɛwà wápiↄ ń wá nɛ́ↄ ń wá àizɛɛↄ yã́ musu.  
\v 22 Ma sosaↄ ń sↄ̃deↄ gbɛaa kíawa aa kàedawázi zɛ́u ibɛɛↄ yã́i oa widɛ̀, asa wá ò kíaɛ wa mɛ̀: Wá Lua ì ↄku gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaì a kĩ́i wɛɛlɛↄla maannↄɛ, ↄ̃ ì a pↄkũma zↄ̃ↄ bↄbↄ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ pãkpàaziↄwa.  
\v 23 Wa lɛyè wa wabikɛ̀ wá Luawa yã́piↄ musu, ↄ̃ a sìwanↄ. 
\p  
\v 24 Ma sa'on dↄaanaↄ sɛ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn kuɛpla ń Selebiao ń Asabiao ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn kwi.  
\v 25 Ɔ̃ ma ã́nusu ń vuao yↄ̃̀nɛ́ kiloowa ń pↄ́ pↄ́ kí ń a lɛdamadeↄ ń aà ìwaↄ ń Isaili pↄ́ kú weↄ a labakɛ̀ wá Lua kpɛ́ gba ũo.  
\v 26 Wa ã́nusu yↄ̃̀nɛ́ kiloowa tↄnu bao ń plao ń ã́nusu pↄ́ↄ tↄnu àaↄ̃ ń vuao tↄnu àaↄ̃.  
\v 27 Vua taↄ ku lↄ mɛ̀n bao, aa kà kiloo swaaↄ̃, mɛ́ mↄgotɛ̃ ta maa tɛkɛaↄ ku mɛ̀n pla, a bɛɛɛ kà vuawa.  
\v 28 Má ònɛ́: Ápiↄ ń pↄ́piↄá Dii pↄ́ɛ. Ãnusu ń vuaoá pↄ́ pↄ́ wà Dii á deziↄ Lua gbàɛ.  
\v 29 À itɛ̃kɛ à pↄ́piↄ dↄ̃́a e a gɛ yↄ̃ kiloowa Dii kpɛ́ kpɛ́nɛↄ guu Yelusalɛũ sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń uabeleↄ wáa.  
\v 30 Ɔ̃ sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ã́nusu ń vuao ń pↄ́ pↄ́ wa yↄ̃̀ kiloowapiↄ sì aa gɛò wá Lua kpɛ́u Yelusalɛũ.  
\v 31 Wa fɛlɛ Aavai, wa da Yelusalɛũ zɛ́u mↄ sɛ̃́ia gↄↄ kuɛpladezĩ. Wá Lua ↄkùwála, à kàedàwázi zɛ́u ibɛɛↄ ń kpã́iwɛliwɛↄ yã́i.  
\v 32 Kɛ́ wa ka Yelusalɛũ, wa kã́mabò we gↄↄ àaↄ̃.  
\v 33 A gↄↄ síiↄ̃de zĩ́ wa ã́nusu ń vuao ń pↄ́piↄ yↄ̃̀ kiloowa wá Lua kpɛ́u, ↄ̃ wá kpà sa'ona Ulia nɛ́ Mɛlemↄwa. Finɛasi nɛ́ Ɛleazaa kuaànↄ ń Yesua nɛ́ Yozabao ń Binui nɛ́ Nↄadiao. Levii buiↄnɛ ḿpii.  
\v 34 Wà apii nào wa yↄ̃̀ kiloowa, ↄ̃ wà a gbia lɛ́ dàlau zĩbeezĩ.  
\v 35 Ɔ̃ zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ ò'o Isailiↄ Luawa, zuswana kuɛpla Isaili bui píi pↄ́ ũ, sãsakao basↄo síiↄ̃sai, sãnɛbↄlↄↄ basiiↄ̃ àaↄ̃sai, blesanaↄ kuɛpla duun awakpabↄ ũ. Wà sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ òò Diiwa píiɛ.  
\v 36 Wà yã́ pↄ́ kía dìlɛ taala kpà aà ìwaↄ ń Uflata baala dↄaanaↄwa, ↄ̃ aa gbãkà Isailiↄnɛ ń Lua kpɛ́ dↄao. 
\c 9  
\s1 Isailiↄ buipãleↄ sɛa nↄ ũ 
\p  
\v 1 Yã́pi kɛa gbɛa kíaↄ mↄ̀ ma kĩ́i aa mɛ̀: Wá gbɛ̃́ↄ ń sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ aai kɛ̃kↄ̃wa ń bui pↄ́ liaawáziↄ ń ń yãbɛ̃ɛkɛaↄo, Kanaaↄ, Itiↄ, Pɛliziↄ, Yebusiↄ, Amↄniↄ, Mↄabuↄ, Egipiↄ ń Amↄleↄ.  
\v 2 Aa nↄsɛ̀ ń guu, aa sɛ̀ ń nɛ́ↄnɛ lↄ. Aa wá bui pↄ́ wá dɛ Lua gbɛ̃́ ũↄ kɛ̀ kↄ̃gbɛ̃ ũ ń bui pↄ́ liaawáziↄ. Kíaↄ ń dↄaanaↄ mɛ́ bↄ̀ Lua kpɛ màa.  
\v 3 Kɛ́ ma yã́pi mà, ma a ula ń ma ulataoo gà má kɛ̃̀, ma a mikãeↄ ń ma lɛkãna kã́eↄ wò. Ɔ̃ ma zↄ̃lɛ, yã́pi dìa.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ yã́ pↄ́ Isailiↄ Lua ò vĩa vĩↄ kã̀aamazi píi zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ bↄa Lua kpɛpi yã́i. Lá yã́pi dìa, ma gↄ̃ zↄ̃lɛa we e sa oosi ogↄↄ.  
\v 5 Kɛ́ sa oosi ogↄↄ kà, ma fɛlɛ mazĩa busaa guu, ma ula ń ma ulataoo kɛ̃a, ↄ̃ ma gɛ kulɛ ma kosowa, ma a ↄ pòopoo Dii ma Luaɛ  
\v 6 ma mɛ̀: 
\p Ma Lua, wí ma kũ, ma gɛɛ gↄ̃̀ kpa ma wɛ́i. Ma Lua, má fↄ̃ wɛ́sɛ mà n gwao, asa wá duuna kùwála, wá tàaeↄ zↄ̃̀ma.  
\v 7 Za wá deziↄ gↄↄ e ń a gbão wá tàae zↄ̃ↄ. Wá duuna yã́i ↄ̃ n wá ná buipãleↄ kíaↄnɛ ń ↄzĩ, wápiↄ ń wá kíaↄ ń wá sa'onaↄ, ↄ̃ aa wá gbɛ̃eↄ dɛ̀dɛ ń fɛ̃ndao, aa wá gbɛ̃eↄ kũ̀ zĩ̀zↄↄ ũ, aa wá pↄ́ↄ nàaa, ↄ̃ wí wá kṹ lá à wá kṹ gbãɛwa.  
\v 8 Dii wá Lua, tia kɛ́wa n wá wɛgwà gĩa yↄↄ, n gbɛ̃́ kↄ̃naↄ tòwɛ̃ɛ, ↄ̃ ń wá gbá tepɛkĩi n kpɛ́u. Wá Lua, ń tò wá oa wèe, n wá lɛ́ ń láo yↄↄ wá zↄbleu.  
\v 9 Wá Lua, baa kɛ́ zↄↄn wá ũ, ni wá tó wá zↄbleuo. Ń tò Pɛɛsiↄ kíaↄ gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀wɛ̃ɛ. N wá lɛ́ ń láo, ↄ̃ wa n kpɛ́ gbooaↄ kɛ̀kɛ wá dↄ̀. Wá Lua, n kàedàwázi Yelusalɛũ ń Yuda bùsuo píi.  
\v 10 Tia kɛ́wa wá Lua, yã́ kpele wá fↄ̃ onɛ lↄi? Asa wa pãkpà n yã́  
\v 11 pↄ́ ń dìlɛ n zↄ̀blena ãnabiↄnɛ aa òↄziɛ. Aa mɛ̀ bùsu pↄ́ wá deziↄ lɛ́ gɛ́ síi dɛ bùsu pↄ́ gbãlɛ̀ bui pↄ́ kú weↄ yãbɛ̃ɛkɛa yã́i ũɛ. An bↄlↄ bùsupi pà za a lɛ́le ń a lɛ́lao an yãbɛ̃ɛkɛa yã́iɛ.  
\v 12 Aa mɛ̀ wásu wà wá nɛnↄɛↄ kpã́sãmáo, mɛ́ wásu ń nↄ sɛ́ wá nɛ́ↄnɛo. Wásu wɛdↄ ń aafia ń ń gwea maaozi bauo, kɛ́ wà e gbãakũ, wí bùsu pↄmaaↄ ble, wà tó wá nɛ́ↄnɛ e gↄↄpii.\f + \fr 9.12 \ft Bↄa 34.12-16, Iko 7.1-4\f* 
\v 13 Yã́piↄ wá lé píi wá vãikɛa ń wá tàae zↄ̃ↄo yã́iɛ. Ń beeo wá Lua, ni ĩadawá e wá duuna lɛ́wao, n gbɛ̃́ kↄ̃naↄ tòwɛ̃ɛ kɛ́wa.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ wa ɛa n yãdilɛaↄ gbòo, wa bui yãbɛ̃ɛkɛnaↄ sɛ̀ nↄ ũ. Lá wá kɛ̀ màa, n pↄ a pawázi, ní wá dɛdɛ míↄmiↄɛ, gbɛ̃́ kↄ̃nae a bↄ lↄo.  
\v 15 Dii Isailiↄ Lua, n yã́ kuɛ, ↄ̃ wa gↄ̃ gbãgbɛ̃ kↄ̃naↄ ũ. Tàaedeↄn wá ũ. A yã́i wá gbɛ̃e a fↄ̃ wɛsɛ à n gwao. 
\c 10  
\s1 Isailiↄ ń duunaↄ oa Luaɛ 
\p  
\v 1 Gↄↄ pↄ́ Ɛzala lɛ́ lousisi màa, a kúlɛa Lua kpɛ́ kpɛɛlɛ, àlɛ ń duunaↄ o Luaɛ, àlɛ ↄ́ↄlↄ, Isailiↄ kã̀aaaàzi dasidasi, gↄ̃ɛↄ ń nↄɛↄ ń nɛ́fɛ̃nɛnaↄ, ↄ̃ aalɛ ↄ́ↄlↄ maamaa.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ Elaũ bui Yeiɛli nɛ́ Sekania fɛ̀lɛ yã'ò Ɛzalaɛ à mɛ̀: Wa bↄ wá Lua kpɛ, wa bui pↄ́ liaawáziↄ sɛ̀ nↄ ũ. Ń beeo bↄkĩi kú wá Isailiↄnɛ e tia.  
\v 3 Wà lɛdoũkɛ ń wá Luao sa, wí nↄɛpiↄ ya ń ń nɛ́ↄ, lá n a lɛdàwáwa, mpi ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa wá Lua yãdilɛaↄ vĩa vĩↄ. Wà kɛ lá aà ikoyã'òwa.  
\v 4 Fɛlɛ! À gↄ̃̀ n yã́ ũɛ. Wa zɛnnↄɛ. Sↄ̃dilɛ ǹ zĩkɛ yã́piwa. 
\p  
\v 5 Ɔ̃ Ɛzala fɛ̀lɛ, a tò kíaↄ ń sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń Isailiↄ píi lɛgbɛ̃̀ yã́pi musu.  
\v 6 Ɔ̃ à gò Lua kpɛ́ kpɛɛlɛ, à gɛ̀ ì Ɛliasibu nɛ́ Yohanani kpɛ́nɛu. I pↄbleo, i imio, kɛ́ àlɛ zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ náaisaikɛ ↄ́ↄlↄ yã́i. 
\p  
\v 7 Ɔ̃ wà kpàwakɛ̀ Yelusalɛũ ń Yuda bùsuo píi wà mɛ̀, zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ aa kãaa Yelusalɛũ píi.  
\v 8 E gↄↄ àaↄ̃ àↄ gɛ́ pai, tó gbɛ̃́ i mↄo, aà àizɛɛↄ gↄ̃̀ Dii pↄ́ ũɛ, wi ade ya bↄ zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ guu. Kíaↄ ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ mɛ́ zɛ̀ò màa.  
\v 9 Ɔ̃ Yuda gↄ̃ɛↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ bui gↄ̃ɛↄ kã̀aa Yelusalɛũ píi e gↄↄ àaↄ̃pi gɛ̀ pàò. Mↄ kɛ̃okwi gↄↄ baode zĩ́ aa zↄ̃lɛa Lua kpɛ́ gãaɛ ḿpii, aalɛ lualua yã́pi ń lou pↄ́ lɛ́ mao yã́i.  
\v 10 Ɔ̃ sa'ona Ɛzala fɛ̀lɛ yã'ònɛ́ à mɛ̀: A bↄ Lua kpɛ, a wá Isailiↄ tàae kã̀fĩ, a buipãleↄ sɛ̀ nↄ ũ.  
\v 11 À á duunaↄ o Dii á deziↄ Luaɛ, í aà pↄeã kɛ sa. À kɛ̃kↄ̃wa ń bui pↄ́ liaaáziↄ ń nↄ pↄ́ á sɛ̀ ń guuↄ.  
\v 12 Bíla wèwà ń lↄↄ gbãao aa mɛ̀: Màaɛ, wá kɛ lá ń òwɛ̃ɛwa.  
\v 13 Ãma wá dasi mɛ́ lou ku, wá fↄ̃ wàↄ zɛa bàasi lao. Wá fↄ̃ yã́pi kɛkɛ gↄↄ do ge gↄↄ plao, asa wá tàae kɛ̀ zↄ̃ↄ yã́pi musu.  
\v 14 Tó wá kíaↄ gↄ̃ la bíla gɛ̃ɛ ũ. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ buipãleↄ sɛ̀ nↄ ũↄ i bↄ wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛo, aai mↄ gↄↄ pↄ́ wa dìlɛnɛ́wa ń ń wɛ̃́lɛ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ń yã́kpalɛkɛnaↄ, wá Lua pↄ i weewá yã́pi musu.  
\v 15 Asaɛli nɛ́ Yonatãa ń Tikeva nɛ́ Yaziao mɛ́ bↄ̀ yã́pi kpɛ ḿpla, ↄ̃ Levii buiↄ Mɛsulaũ ń Sabetaio zɛ̀ńnↄ. 
\p  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ zĩ̀zↄ pↄ́ sùↄ kɛ̀ lá wa òwa. Sa'ona Ɛzala uabeleↄ sɛ̀ daɛdaɛ mɛ̀ndodo. À ń tↄ́ dàlau píi. Mↄ kwide gↄↄ sɛ̃́ia zĩ́ ↄ̃ gbɛ̃́piↄ zↄ̃̀lɛ yã́pi gwàgwa.  
\v 17 Mↄ sɛ̃́ia gↄↄ sɛ̃́ia zĩ́ aa buipãle sɛnapiↄ yã́ gwàgwa aa làa píi. 
\s1 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa buipãle nↄ sɛ̀ↄ 
\p  
\v 18 Sa'ona pↄ́ aa buipãle nↄ sɛ̀ↄn kɛ: Yozada nɛ́ Yesua buiↄ ń a dãunaɛ beeↄ Maasea, Ɛliɛzɛɛ, Yalibu, Gedalia.  
\v 19 Aa ↄdà kↄ̃ ↄu aa mɛ̀ wa ń nↄpiↄ yá, ↄ̃ an baade sãsa kpà ń tàae fĩabobↄ ũ.  
\v 20 Imɛɛ buiↄ Anani ń Zebadiao.  
\v 21 Aliũ buiↄ Maasea, Ɛlia, Semaia, Yeiɛli, Uzia.  
\v 22 Pasuu buiↄ Ɛlioenai, Maasea, Isimaɛla, Nɛtanɛli, Yozaba, Ɛlasa.  
\v 23 Levii buiↄ Yozaba, Simɛi, Kelaia pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Kelita, Petaia, Yuda, Ɛliɛzɛɛ.  
\v 24 Lɛ̀sina Ɛliasibu ń bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ Saluũ ń Teleũo ń Ulio. 
\p  
\v 25 Isaili kĩni pↄ́ aa buipãle nↄ sɛ̀ↄn kɛ: Palↄsi buiↄ Lamia, Izia, Malakia, Miamɛ, Ɛleazaa, Malakia, Benaia.  
\v 26 Elaũ buiↄ Matania, Zakali, Yeiɛli, Abadi, Yelemↄ, Ɛlia.  
\v 27 Zatu buiↄ Ɛlioenai, Ɛliasibu, Matania, Yelemↄ, Zabada, Aziza.  
\v 28 Bebai buiↄ Yohanani, Anania, Zabai, Atalai.  
\v 29 Bani buiↄ Mɛsulaũ, Maluku, Adaia, Yasubu, Seali, Yelemↄ.  
\v 30 Paata Mↄabu buiↄ Adena, Kelala, Benaia, Maasea, Matania, Bezalɛli, Binui, Manase.  
\v 31 Aliũ buiↄ Ɛliɛzɛɛ, Isia, Semaia, Simɛↄ,  
\v 32 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ, Maluku, Semalia.  
\v 33 Asuũ buiↄ Matenai, Matata, Zabada, Ɛlifele, Yelemai, Manase, Simɛi.  
\v 34 Bani buiↄ Maadai, Amlaũ, Uɛli,  
\v 35 Benaia, Bedea, Kelui,  
\v 36 Vania, Mɛlemↄ, Ɛliasibu,  
\v 37 Matania, Matenai, Yaasu.  
\v 38 Binui buiↄ Simɛi,  
\v 39 Selemia, Natã, Adaia,  
\v 40 Manadebai, Sasai, Salai,  
\v 41 Azalɛli, Selemia, Semalia,  
\v 42 Saluũ, Amalia, Yosɛfu.  
\v 43 Nɛbo buiↄ Yeiɛli, Matitia, Zabada, Zebina, Yadai, Yoɛli, Benaia.  
\v 44 Gbɛ̃́piↄ buipãle nↄ sɛ̀ɛ ḿpii, mɛ́ an nↄpi keeↄ nɛ́ↄ ì'ińnↄ.